data.description: Welcome to Summer Hill at Eastlake Vistas! This move-in-ready condo offers an open concept, spacious kitchen, balcony, and a 2-car garage. As a resident, enjoy exclusive access to two pools, BBQ areas, a clubhouse, and a fitness center.The unbeatable location puts you close to top-rated schools, restaurants, retail, and Otay Ranch Mall. Nature lovers will appreciate Mountain Hawk Park and nearby trails, while golf enthusiasts can tee off at the Enagic Golf Club. Don't miss this chance to embrace the finest living in Eastlake Vistas.Your new beginning awaits! Seller offers INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN FOR SIGNIFICANT SAVINGS. FHA/VA approved. Don't miss out!
